    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example has been mechanically sorted with a comprehensive dual-VANOS overhaul and preventative rod bearing replacement using VAC coated shells. The chassis integrity is secured via rear subframe reinforcement plates, mitigating common floor-pan fatigue under high torque loads. Power is managed through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory variable M differential lock. The suspension features refreshed polyurethane bushings and Bilstein dampers for optimized turn-in and transient response. A mechanically robust specimen with dialed-in drivetrain dynamics, ready for the B-roads.",
